      <title>石油消费者趁期货暴跌锁定更便宜的石油桶</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-08/oil-consumers-pounce-on-futures-slump-to-lock-in-cheaper-barrels</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于本周的价格下滑使得对冲成本降低，石油消费者抓住了锁定能源成本上涨的机会。]]></description>
